# spec.plan — PitchTwin

## Project Identity
- **Name**: PitchTwin
- **Tagline**: Your CV, came to life.
- **Type**: Multi-agent AI system
- **Target**: Technology consulting firms

---

## Problem Statement
Consultants at tech firms must tailor their CVs, bios, and talking points for every client pitch. This is done manually, under deadline pressure, leading to:
- Inconsistent output quality
- Wasted senior talent time
- Poor client first impressions

---

## Solution
PitchTwin automates the entire pitch preparation and pre-meeting experience via a 7-agent pipeline:

1. **Proposal Package Generation** — Tailored CV, bio, talking points, gap analysis
2. **Interactive Client Twin** — A text-based conversational agent representing the consultant, grounded strictly in real profile data
3. **Consultant Debrief** — Auto-generated summary of what the client asked and cared about, delivered before the first real meeting

---

## Core User Flows

### Flow A: BD Manager / Consultant triggers a new proposal
1. Login to consultant dashboard
2. Select or upload consultant profile
3. Paste client brief + company name
4. System runs pipeline → delivers proposal package in <5 min

### Flow B: Client interacts with the twin
1. Receives unique link
2. Opens chat interface in browser
3. Asks free-form questions about consultant
4. Twin responds grounded in real profile data only

### Flow C: Debrief delivery
1. Client ends session (or closes browser)
2. Debrief Agent auto-triggers on transcript
3. Summary report sent to consultant dashboard

---

## Agent Roster

| Agent | Role | Input | Output |
|---|---|---|---|
| Profile Agent | Parse + structure consultant profile | Raw profile (text/JSON) | Structured skills, experience, projects |
| Client Research Agent | Analyze client brief | Brief + company name | Industry context, challenges, tech stack |
| Matching Agent | Rank relevance | Profile data + client context | Ranked relevance map |
| Writer Agent | Generate proposal artifacts | Relevance map + client tone | Tailored CV, bio, talking points |
| Gap Agent | Identify mismatches | Client requirements + profile | Gap list + framing suggestions |
| Persona Agent | Build conversational twin | Full profile + matched experience | LLM-powered chat twin |
| Debrief Agent | Summarize client conversation | Chat transcript | Structured debrief report |

### Orchestration Rules
- **Parallel**: Profile Agent + Client Research Agent run concurrently (Python threading)
- **Sequential**: Matching → Writer → Gap → (package delivered); Persona Agent initialized after matching
- **Trigger**: Debrief Agent fires on session end event

---

## Data Model

### consultant_profile
```json
{
  "id": "uuid",
  "name": "string",
  "raw_profile": "text",
  "structured": {
    "skills": [],
    "experience": [],
    "projects": []
  },
  "tone_markers": "string",
  "created_at": "timestamp"
}
```

### proposal
```json
{
  "id": "uuid",
  "consultant_id": "uuid",
  "client_brief": "text",
  "company_name": "string",
  "tailored_cv": "text",
  "bio": "text",
  "talking_points": [],
  "gap_analysis": "text",
  "relevance_map": "object",
  "status": "pending|ready",
  "created_at": "timestamp"
}
```

### twin_session
```json
{
  "id": "uuid",
  "proposal_id": "uuid",
  "transcript": [],
  "debrief": "text",
  "status": "active|ended",
  "created_at": "timestamp"
}
```

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Choice | Reason |
|---|---|---|
| Language | Python 3.11 | Team familiarity, rich AI libs |
| Web Framework | Flask | Lightweight, fast to wire up |
| LLM | Google Gemini API (gemini-1.5-flash) | Free tier, strong quality |
| LLM Alt | Groq + Llama 3 | Faster inference, also free |
| Orchestration | Python asyncio + threading | No extra framework needed |
| Storage | SQLite (prod) / JSON files (dev) | Zero-config, portable |
| Frontend | Flask Jinja2 templates + plain CSS | Minimal, shippable fast |
| Deployment | Docker + docker-compose | Reproducible, simple |

---

## Non-Goals (v1)
- No audio/video
- No authentication system (token-based link sharing only)
- No real-time streaming (polling acceptable)
- No external email sending (debrief shown in dashboard)

---

## Success Criteria
- End-to-end happy path runs in <5 min
- Client twin refuses to invent experience not in profile
- Debrief fires automatically on session end
- System runs fully in Docker with single `docker-compose up`
